title: NFL Week 11 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 11 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap every Sunday game from Week 11 in the NFL and debate which teams are in the driver seat for a playoff spot.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
